From: Marco Grandis <grandis@dima.unige.it>
Subject: categories: Weak cubical categories
Date: Fri, 25 Jul 2008 16:46:21 +0200
To: categories@mta.ca
Sender: cat-dist@mta.ca
Precedence: bulk
Message-Id: <E1KMPKs-00024w-KS@mailserv.mta.ca>
